metadata.name: Warp speed ENGAGE
metadata.description:
Captains log  
Stardate 11112022

After a successful experimental fueling proces with minting claims and onboarding new collectors as crew for this mission. The warp engines are fueled and the warp core is primed for maximum speed.

Thus the Enterprise is ready for it's voyage through NFT Space! Coordinates are set, navigating the blockchain was a difficult task, but we are ready for Web3. 

Mr. Sulu, take us out

Warp speed...ENGAGE!
